{"tid":966065,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【2018香港票房】《棟篤特工》成華語片冠軍 《復仇者3》全年最賣座","createTime":"2019-01-02T13:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T07:03:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c73ccd00d27086e081846e895adfb839cd8ddf","tid":966065,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190102/s00009/9360cc86e7223a7565dda06b8524dad2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190102%2Fs00009%2F9360cc86e7223a7565dda06b8524dad2.jpg&h=3e7e9b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190102/s00009/9362baa6a170bb65d35a60db385c8823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190102%2Fs00009%2F9362baa6a170bb65d35a60db385c8823.jpg&h=e732cc19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190102/s00009/9363cd8401c9ef388ca0594c578f43f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190102%2Fs00009%2F9363cd8401c9ef388ca0594c578f43f2.jpg&h=c631d18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港票房有限公司今日公布2018年的香港電影票房成績，去年首輪上映的電影總數為353部，香港電影佔53部，非香港電影佔300部，中西票房總收入19.5億港元，與2017年同期的總收入18.5億港元比較，上升5.57%。<br />\n<br />\n當中由黃子華及佘詩曼合演的《棟篤特工》，以4470萬港元票房，成為2018年華語片冠軍，第二位是周潤發及郭富城合演的《無雙》（3440萬港元），第三位是賀歲片《我的情敵女婿》（1742萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n至於外語片方面，Marvel電影《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》以1.53億港元票房稱霸，成為外語片冠軍兼2018年全年總票房冠軍，遠遠拋離第二位的《侏羅紀世界：迷失國度》（8864萬港元）及第三位的《超人特工隊2》（7120萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1546435890878&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20190102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1546435890878%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20190102&d=GQs%2F0oZ20mHpatel3Nm0oxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=d3010532\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1546435890878%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20190102&h=117a0726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1546435890878&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20190102</a>"},{"pid":"bce627f32b4bdf7110b072c808a62de4eb9845b7","tid":966065,"uid":66540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"華語片冠軍都唔及西片排第十既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a43b941c432fb269b61bb4affb1dfe5b716d8e","tid":966065,"uid":16092,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"L風暴 見過朗豪坊嗰條換票証人龍就知條數唔洗信<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194662a8ef9b611dbced1941d0b092493a2c4f4d","tid":966065,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce627f32b4bdf7110b072c808a62de4eb9845b7","tid":966065,"uid":66540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"華語片冠軍都唔及西片排第十既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"排第十唔係西片，係韓片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771269b5461fe4c21f76ced2ef048531f4c34c19","tid":966065,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"建國大孽呢？"},{"pid":"304e0bcf5e3361deec2ab5fd4c2abe48957cb167","tid":966065,"uid":3567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05a43b941c432fb269b61bb4affb1dfe5b716d8e","tid":966065,"uid":16092,"like":13,"dislike"